dmca.title: DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google
dmca.sender_name: Hotels of the Rich and Famous

works.description:
Hal Sparks image by Radko Keleman is used
 
on my website with permission from Radko Keleman after a referral from the
 
Actor himself to the Photographer whom I both have permission to use the  
image.

I submitted this earlier but did not get a confirmation email so I am  
trying again. These sites steal my image then steal my rank. This image  
used to rank #3 on the 1st page for google image search now it ranks on
the  
3rd page! They steal my image then destroy the rank!
